1
00:01:10,360 --> 00:01:11,160
Huang Xiaoyun,

2
00:01:11,160 --> 00:01:13,160
we'd like to ask you some questions.

3
00:01:13,320 --> 00:01:16,250
Is there any bad blood between Tian Liang and Lu Yang?

4
00:01:17,160 --> 00:01:18,039
Actually,

5
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:20,340
it's because of me.

6
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:22,770
You know Tian Liang?

7
00:01:25,800 --> 00:01:26,760
He's an animal.

8
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:28,720
He...

9
00:01:30,720 --> 00:01:31,760
bullied me.

10
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:37,880
Does Lu Yang know about this?

11
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:41,970
Can you tell us in detail

12
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,330
what exactly happened?

13
00:01:44,039 --> 00:01:44,880
That day,

14
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:47,440
Aunt Xia Lin forgot her keys.

15
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:49,930
I was passing by on my way to school,

16
00:01:50,160 --> 00:01:51,690
so I went to give them to her.

17
00:01:57,800 --> 00:01:58,240
Hello.

18
00:01:58,640 --> 00:01:59,880
I'm looking for Xia Lin.

19
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:00,280
Okay.

20
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:01,400
Coach Tian,

21
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:04,060
someone is looking for your member, Xia Lin.

22
00:02:04,440 --> 00:02:04,920
Hello.

23
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:07,290
Are you looking for Xia Lin?

24
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:09,840
Her keys.

25
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:11,320
Keys.

26
00:02:14,640 --> 00:02:15,280
Not yet.

27
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:18,760
Just leave them here.

28
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:26,050
Xiaoyun.

29
00:02:26,920 --> 00:02:27,520
Xiaoyun.

30
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:29,760
What's wrong?

31
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:32,380
Nothing. What happened to your hand?

32
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,040
Are you okay?

33
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,680
I got bullied.

34
00:02:37,160 --> 00:02:38,120
Who bullied you?

35
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:39,890
Tell me who bullied you.

36
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:48,079
So after this incident,

37
00:02:48,480 --> 00:02:50,400
Lu Yang started to hate Tian Liang,

38
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:50,800
right?

39
00:02:54,079 --> 00:02:55,600
Lu Yang knew about this

40
00:02:56,200 --> 00:02:57,260
and was very angry.

41
00:02:59,880 --> 00:03:01,940
Could Lu Yang have killed Tian Liang?

42
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:03,570
Don't overthink it.

43
00:03:04,920 --> 00:03:06,380
If that's really the case,

44
00:03:07,600 --> 00:03:09,260
then this is all because of me.

45
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:10,520
We

46
00:03:10,880 --> 00:03:13,140
are just asking you about the situation.

47
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:14,720
You don't need to put others' mistakes

48
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:15,840
on yourself.

49
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:17,040
Relax.

50
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:18,800
Thank you for your cooperation.

51
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:21,329
We'll contact you again if anything comes up.

52
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:23,450
Let's go.

53
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:26,079
Thank you for your cooperation.

54
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,000
You just went to the gym.

55
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:45,800
Why give such an expensive gift?

56
00:03:46,079 --> 00:03:48,079
Your relationship must be special.

57
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:55,320
Linlin.

58
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:57,760
What's wrong?

59
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:02,400
The police came to my school to find me today

60
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:03,520
and said

61
00:04:04,760 --> 00:04:06,520
my fitness coach is missing.

62
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:09,320
I'm a little scared.

63
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:11,210
Does his disappearance

64
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:12,880
have anything to do with you?

65
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:16,899
Of course it has nothing to do with me.

66
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:18,880
But he's someone I know after all.

67
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:21,240
It's inexplicable that he went missing.

68
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:22,770
I just feel a bit terrified.

69
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:24,640
Alright.

70
00:04:27,520 --> 00:04:28,450
Don't be afraid.

71
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:31,240
It has nothing to do with you anyway.

72
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:35,560
Let's go to sleep.

73
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:41,290
Don't turn off the light, okay?

74
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:43,680
Okay.

75
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,120
Tian Liang.

76
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,440
You told me to follow him.

77
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:06,880
Now he's dead.

78
00:05:07,840 --> 00:05:09,400
If I tell the police,

79
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:11,480
you won't be able to get away with it either.

80
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:13,640
He's not exactly a good guy.

81
00:05:14,200 --> 00:05:15,400
But murder is murder.

82
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,980
The killer deserves to pay for it.

83
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:19,800
What do you think?

84
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:26,160
Lu Yang indeed had a strong motive to kill Tian Liang.

85
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:29,420
It's highly likely he killed Tian Liang for Huang Xiaoyun.

86
00:05:29,520 --> 00:05:30,640
So that means

87
00:05:30,960 --> 00:05:32,960
Huang Xiaoyun saw Tian Liang first.

88
00:05:33,520 --> 00:05:35,680
After Lu Yang took Xiaoyun home,

89
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:37,480
he ran into Tian Liang again,

90
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,440
followed him,

91
00:05:38,760 --> 00:05:40,760
and beat him up at the street corner.

92
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:43,120
How did the questioning with Xia Lin go?

93
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:44,780
She didn't admit to the photo.

94
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:46,770
But looking at her expression,

95
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:48,980
I suspect she lied.

96
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:51,650
There are too many suspicious points.

97
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:54,280
Let's go question Lu Yang now.

98
00:05:54,280 --> 00:05:54,810
Let's go.

99
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,800
Zhao, help Xiao Li sort out the transcript.

100
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:57,800
How long has it been?

101
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:58,200
Okay.

102
00:05:58,800 --> 00:05:59,730
Be more careful.

103
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:01,280
Thanks, Zhao.

104
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,159
Captain Shen.

105
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:04,010
It feels like more than one person came into the room yesterday.

106
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:06,090
There are marks.

107
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:08,610
But the forensics colleagues said

108
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:10,360
there was no struggle.

109
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:11,020
Indeed not.

110
00:07:11,960 --> 00:07:13,120
And judging by this shoe print,

111
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:14,980
it should belong to a young woman.

112
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:16,240
Please continue.

113
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:17,720
When elderly people walk,

114
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:19,120
they lift their entire foot high,

115
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:20,840
usually landing on the whole sole.

116
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:22,480
This shoe print is clearly not like that.

117
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:23,810
Young people walk fast,

118
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,600
landing heavily on the ball of the foot.

119
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:27,080
Also, women have wider hip joints,

120
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:30,210
so the parallel distance between their feet is greater.

121
00:07:31,640 --> 00:07:32,640
It's almost dawn.

122
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,159
Call Zhao and Li

123
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:37,320
to start the interrogation.

124
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:45,240
They don't live around here.

125
00:07:45,520 --> 00:07:46,980
Did any strangers come by?

126
00:07:47,200 --> 00:07:47,760
Master.

127
00:07:50,400 --> 00:07:51,200
We have a clue.

128
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:52,159
Ma'am.

129
00:07:52,840 --> 00:07:54,000
Do you know the person in this room?

130
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:55,040
I do.

131
00:07:55,080 --> 00:07:55,320
No entry.

132
00:07:55,320 --> 00:07:56,000
But recently,

133
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,260
he seemed to be in debt.

134
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:59,000
There were always debt collectors coming to his door.

135
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,600
No entry.

136
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:01,920
Do you think he might have taken his own life?

137
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:03,880
No entry.

138
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:05,040
Did anyone come to this room yesterday?

139
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:05,840
Someone

140
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,440
went in with some liquor.

141
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:09,120
Do you remember what time it was?

142
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:10,720
I came home last night

143
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:12,170
at 10:00 p.m.

144
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:14,240
Yes, around 10:00 p.m.

145
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:16,460
Does anyone have any other clues?

146
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,040
I don't think so.

147
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:19,680
Tell us anytime if you remember anything.

148
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,360
You can also tell these two.

149
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:21,240
They are our colleagues.

150
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:21,880
They will let us know.

151
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:22,840
Okay.

152
00:08:22,840 --> 00:08:23,480
All right.

153
00:08:24,640 --> 00:08:26,240
He was so young to pass away.

154
00:08:26,520 --> 00:08:27,200
What a pity.

155
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,420
I'll leave a...

156
00:08:37,280 --> 00:08:37,880
Sister Na.

157
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,059
How is it going?

158
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,460
It's definitely fine.

159
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:42,690
Don't worry.

160
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:44,120
Okay then.

161
00:08:48,880 --> 00:08:50,080
Captain Jiang, Captain Shen.

162
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:52,480
There are footprints and tire tracks here.

163
00:08:57,960 --> 00:09:00,400
The car stopped here briefly before leaving.

164
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:01,480
Xiao Li, take a picture.

165
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:01,960
Okay.

166
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:04,400
Someone definitely came yesterday.

167
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:05,560
Only one footprint.

168
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:09,060
Where did he come from and where did he go?

169
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:11,040
Looks like an adult male.

170
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,560
Could it be the killer?

171
00:09:13,680 --> 00:09:14,410
I'm not sure.

172
00:09:15,040 --> 00:09:17,080
The direction is towards Lu Yang's house.

173
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:18,080
It's very likely.

174
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:19,820
Xiao Li.

175
00:09:19,920 --> 00:09:20,780
How about this.

176
00:09:20,880 --> 00:09:22,360
Interview nearby residents immediately,

177
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:23,120
then verify.

178
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,840
Contact the victim's family and school.

179
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:25,240
Okay.

180
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:25,840
Let's go.

181
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:26,360
Zhao.

182
00:09:26,520 --> 00:09:27,000
Okay.

183
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:28,680
Notify the Technical Department.

184
00:09:28,680 --> 00:09:29,160
Okay.

185
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:38,360
Go,

186
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:39,420
hurry up and get in.

187
00:09:41,880 --> 00:09:42,800
Coming.

188
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:43,600
Coming.

189
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:45,060
Let's go ask for the money.

190
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:51,260
What are you

191
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:52,400
doing?

192
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:54,720
You signed the contract yourselves.

193
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:55,960
It's not like we won't pay you.

194
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:56,690
Your company

195
00:09:56,880 --> 00:09:57,920
violently forces demolitions,

196
00:09:57,920 --> 00:09:59,160
owes relocation funds,

197
00:09:59,160 --> 00:10:00,520
and violates the contract.

198
00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:01,000
Exactly.

199
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:01,530
Exactly.

200
00:10:01,680 --> 00:10:03,880
We paid you the relocation funds according to the regulations.

201
00:10:03,880 --> 00:10:05,760
We also showed you the building plans.

202
00:10:05,760 --> 00:10:07,280
Why are you still making a scene here?

203
00:10:07,280 --> 00:10:08,520
We went to your company,

204
00:10:08,520 --> 00:10:09,280
but got kicked out.

205
00:10:09,280 --> 00:10:10,240
We submitted a complaint

206
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:11,400
but never got any feedback.

207
00:10:11,400 --> 00:10:12,400
Tell us what to do!

208
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:13,520
What should we do? Tell us!

209
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:14,080
What should we do?

210
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:15,680
Everyone, please calm down.

211
00:10:15,680 --> 00:10:17,440
Once I investigate this thoroughly,

212
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:18,520
I will resolve it for you as soon as possible,

213
00:10:18,520 --> 00:10:18,850
okay?

214
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:20,240
Stop trying to fool us with nice words.

215
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,760
You said the same thing during the relocation.

216
00:10:21,760 --> 00:10:22,680
It's been half a year.

217
00:10:22,680 --> 00:10:24,720
We only got half of the compensation.

218
00:10:24,720 --> 00:10:25,640
Yes, exactly!

219
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:28,040
How about this, give me some time

220
00:10:28,280 --> 00:10:30,200
to investigate the matter thoroughly.

221
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:32,320
I will solve it for you as soon as possible.

222
00:10:32,320 --> 00:10:33,400
If you don't believe me,

223
00:10:33,400 --> 00:10:34,720
look, here is my business card.

224
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:35,360
Take it.

225
00:10:36,160 --> 00:10:36,720
If

226
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:39,240
it still can't be solved, you can sue me.

227
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:40,240
You go back first,

228
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:40,800
okay?

229
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:42,200
Are you all relieved now?

230
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:43,720
Okay, we'll trust you one more time.

231
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:44,920
We will wait for you. Let's go.

232
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:45,560
We trust you this time.

233
00:10:45,560 --> 00:10:47,420
It hasn't been solved for so long.

234
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:51,130
These unruly people

235
00:10:51,640 --> 00:10:53,300
only know how to make trouble.

236
00:11:00,560 --> 00:11:02,620
I'll go check the construction site.

237
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:18,000
Ye Qiming believed the words of a few villagers

238
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,400
and went to the construction site to investigate.

239
00:11:19,400 --> 00:11:21,880
For Ye Qiming's serious spirit,

240
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:23,600
we should praise him.

241
00:11:24,480 --> 00:11:25,480
Praise him?

242
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:51,720
Mr. Wu.

243
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:56,320
Chief.

244
00:11:56,880 --> 00:11:57,360
Chief.

245
00:11:57,760 --> 00:11:58,960
What exactly is going on?

246
00:11:58,960 --> 00:12:00,420
We just found the suspect,

247
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:01,840
and now he's dead.

248
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:03,600
It was our mistake.

249
00:12:04,520 --> 00:12:05,360
A mistake?

250
00:12:06,280 --> 00:12:07,810
It's a dereliction of duty.

251
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:10,280
Sit down.

252
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:20,250
What I want is progress on the case.

253
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:21,930
How is Tian Liang's case

254
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:22,920
progressing?

255
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:25,200
We have been investigating it diligently.

256
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:27,800
I know you've been investigating diligently.

257
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:29,400
The suspect is dead.

258
00:12:30,680 --> 00:12:32,280
The problem will be even bigger.

259
00:12:32,280 --> 00:12:33,210
Do you know that?

260
00:12:33,680 --> 00:12:35,480
How many eyes are on us right now?

261
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,080
Now even the media

262
00:12:37,400 --> 00:12:38,600
have gotten the news.

263
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:42,400
We must be responsible to the people of Tongjiang.

264
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:45,600
We need to give an explanation to our superiors.

265
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:46,330
Understood.

266
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:48,200
The death of the suspect

267
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:50,080
is something none of us wanted to see.

268
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:53,480
But the incident happened on the same day as your interrogation.

269
00:12:53,480 --> 00:12:56,000
Is it a conspiracy or a coincidence?

270
00:12:58,200 --> 00:12:58,760
Chief.

271
00:13:00,920 --> 00:13:04,850
I suggest we combine Tian Liang and Lu Yang's cases for investigation.

272
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:06,730
Alright.

273
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:08,120
Hurry up.

274
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:08,970
Yes, sir.

275
00:14:11,280 --> 00:14:13,610
How did Mr. Ye get hit by the falling rebar?

276
00:14:13,760 --> 00:14:14,200
Yes.

277
00:14:14,560 --> 00:14:16,020
Mr. Ye got hit by the rebar.

278
00:14:16,200 --> 00:14:17,560
Hurry up and call an ambulance!

279
00:14:17,560 --> 00:14:19,960
Call an ambulance. I'll call an ambulance!

280
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:27,720
Qiming, change your clothes back.

281
00:14:27,720 --> 00:14:28,600
The doctor wouldn't let you.

282
00:14:28,600 --> 00:14:29,800
I'm not wearing them.

283
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:31,480
How could you be so careless?

284
00:14:32,400 --> 00:14:33,530
I just find it weird.

285
00:14:34,040 --> 00:14:34,800
From the top of the building,

286
00:14:34,800 --> 00:14:36,600
how could a steel pipe fall down?

287
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:38,760
Yeah.

288
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:40,440
Everything was fine.

289
00:14:40,520 --> 00:14:42,640
How could this suddenly happen?

290
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:44,680
I need to go back and check.

291
00:14:44,680 --> 00:14:45,120
No.

292
00:14:45,240 --> 00:14:46,100
The doctor said

293
00:14:46,280 --> 00:14:46,960
you can't be discharged.

294
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:48,160
You need to rest well.

295
00:14:48,200 --> 00:14:49,280
I can't stay here.

296
00:14:49,400 --> 00:14:49,920
No way.

297
00:14:50,040 --> 00:14:51,900
Hurry up and change your clothes.

298
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:52,840
Get some rest.

299
00:14:52,840 --> 00:14:53,800
I'll head back first.

300
00:14:53,800 --> 00:14:55,480
Qiming, why don't you listen?

301
00:14:55,480 --> 00:14:56,320
No, no.

302
00:14:58,200 --> 00:14:59,130
Sister-in-law.

303
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:01,290
Are you alright?

304
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:02,640
You scared us to death.

305
00:15:03,160 --> 00:15:03,680
Yu Na.

306
00:15:04,560 --> 00:15:07,720
Can you stop letting Qiming go to the construction site from now on?

307
00:15:07,720 --> 00:15:08,640
Yes.

308
00:15:08,840 --> 00:15:10,080
Health comes first.

309
00:15:10,280 --> 00:15:11,010
Don't worry.

310
00:15:11,280 --> 00:15:12,680
I'll take care of Tongda.

311
00:15:13,200 --> 00:15:14,560
I'm heading back to the company now.

312
00:15:14,560 --> 00:15:16,160
You guys come over together.

313
00:15:16,440 --> 00:15:17,040
Qiming,

314
00:15:17,600 --> 00:15:18,530
sister-in-law.

315
00:15:20,640 --> 00:15:21,760
I will handle it.

316
00:15:34,680 --> 00:15:37,920
I pulled up the footage from three surveillance cameras near Lu Yang's house.

317
00:15:37,920 --> 00:15:39,680
The one facing

318
00:15:39,760 --> 00:15:40,880
the street by Lu Yang's house

319
00:15:40,880 --> 00:15:41,680
is broken,

320
00:15:42,160 --> 00:15:44,440
and it happened to break just last night.

321
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:47,130
What a coincidence.

322
00:15:47,920 --> 00:15:49,980
It really doesn't look like suicide.

323
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:53,280
Did the other two cameras catch anything?

324
00:15:53,280 --> 00:15:53,760
Look.

325
00:15:57,040 --> 00:15:57,370
Stop.

326
00:15:58,600 --> 00:15:59,160
Rewind.

327
00:16:02,560 --> 00:16:04,000
This car looks familiar.
